# Project rules

This repo's conventions (architecture, layer responsibilities, naming, error handling,
migration checklist) live in `AGENTS.md` at the repo root — Cursor loads it
automatically. Do not duplicate that content here; only add Cursor-specific
automation/rules in this folder.

Shared skills (e.g. `backend-development`) live in `.agents/skills/` and are
available to the agent for maintenance, debugging, and implementation tasks.
